title: Game Key Revealer
description:
Game Key Revealer v1.0.2


Game Key Revealer, reveals the CD-Key and Serials for installed games on computer. 
If you lost legal CD-Keys or Serials of your purchased games, you can find them with Game Key Revealer.


Features:
- Displays over 500 games
- Save to Text or Word (Word XP/2003/2007 only)
- Print
- Displays for 64bit-Edition releases


Notes: - If gives "DLL Error" on Windows 98/ME please download the "MSVBVM60.DLL" file 
         from http://cakirbey.googlepages.com and copy to same directory with Game Key Revealer.
       - If gives an error on Windows XP please download the "MSSTDFMT.DLL" file 
         from http://cakirbey.googlepages.com and perform the descriptions.


Supported Operating Systems:
Windows 98/ME/XP/2003/Vista
